front.title: •Wooof (V)
front.gametext: Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. May deploy with any cruiser using Combat Response. While aboard an [Independent] starship, opponent's battle and weapon destiny draws here are -1.
front.lore: Kadas'sa'Nikto. One of Jabba's best pilots. Often pilots Jabba's space yacht. Smuggler. Prefers to be flying combat starfighters.
